reviewText: It just doesn't get any better than Grand Master Song!

A good video . They go over each hold in great detail . Different camera angles and speeds , showing close ups of the hand positions and footwork . If you're trying to learn Hapkido from home , or just reviewing , these DVDs by Master Song are some of the best for the money in my opinion .
Excellent instructional DVD; it has taken my fighting skills to the next level!
